            <h3>
                <span class="comment-vote">
                    <span id="c-813721442" class="vote-count">0</span>
                        <a href="javascript:;" id="btn-813721442" class="j a_show_login" data-cid="813721442">有用</a>
                </span>
                <span class="comment-info">
                    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/3897218/">fighterjzh</a>
                        <span class="user-stars allstar40 rating" title="推荐"></span>
                    <span>2014-06-06</span>
                </span>
            </h3>
            <p class="comment-content">通史类，文笔不错，但感觉分析还不够透彻，对这段历史不太清楚的通过本书可以有个大致的了解，但作者似乎还驾驭不了这么大的题材。</p>
        </div>
    </li>

                
    <li class="comment-item" data-cid="807251745">
